These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, puzzles
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, journalist
1. the entrepreneur is in an even position##4
2. the journalist is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | puzzles | skydiving |
| Job     | journalist    | entrepreneur   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, surfing
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | mirinda | hot-chocolate        |
| Sport      | volleyball  | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, classical
There are 2 different nationalities: german, dutch
1. the german is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | d&b |
| Nationality   | german | dutch |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, juice
There 2 different types of food: kale, raspberry
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person eating raspberry is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | tea      | juice |
| Food       | kale | raspberry    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
