 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, biathlon
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike
1. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | biathlon | rowing  |
| Transport   | quad-bike  | helicopter |

